                        "name": "Two Actions"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You flick a corner of the card, as if casting aside a tiny pest or fleck of filth from its surface; you cast *Abyssal plague*. If you are at least 15th-level, you can instead choose to cast *spiritual epidemic*. Regardless of which spell you cast, the level of the spell is half your level, rounded down (minimum 6th level), and the save DC is equal to your class DC.",
                    "links": [
                        {
